\" /> <br />\n但用下腦都知道條女係咩料，正如上面巴打都講過，拍咁撚多次拖，都結唔到婚。<br />\nd人仲封佢為咩好女友，佢性格都唔好得去邊<br />\n我既結論係洪永城都唔係d咩好男人，唐詩詠都唔係d咩好女人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2535b614a43bcbe0af6af4dec2a688a3bea305e","tid":511210,"uid":12302,"like":160,"dislike":2,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/apis/web/viaphoto2/74/7439449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fapis%2Fweb%2Fviaphoto2%2F74%2F7439449&h=c31dde35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57a28cf3c04345c11828d1bd7fed7ac8ee4916ca","tid":511210,"uid":79658,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"a0b3c02ab708f587da297a79efd9f9b4c62dcd97","tid":511210,"uid":29523,"like":32,"dislike":6,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"0fbb0d75a178dfed2dfffeab502fa0364f611c6b","tid":511210,"uid":138427,"like":149,"dislike":7,"score":142,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"本身條女性格應該有問題既，唔係點會拍咁多次都收皮"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"釣金龜，愈釣要求愈高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"要釣就揀咗啲金融才俊中坑埋單啦<br />\n要同崔建邦拍咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢性格有問題都話可能啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2e84e3442c683f71b85412caf24105e9d3621d","tid":511210,"uid":85819,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50c5db40675ebc1c88aedef8e11a3cca551b0015","tid":511210,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"扮豬食老虎"},{"pid":"fe9a2da0bdef01b4a5a0db7bd211f51d1950e94b","tid":511210,"uid":83698,"like":66,"dislike":3,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTi